reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater very cute and comfortable, noting it doesn't irritate sensitive skin and is soft without being bulky.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice and warm
items.body: Cute and fits perfectly I got size xl I am 5’4 and weight 189 pounds. I am heavy at the top so my breast fit right in the cups. Read more
items.author: Fay

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for the season
items.body: Super cute love the quality it’s thick. The only thing I did not like was it did not stay off the shoulder. Read more
items.author: Jenny Arely Fonseca Campos

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Super stylish top
items.body: I ordered this top in blue in size small. It arrived in great condition and looks of quality. I took a star way because even for this style of top it is too big. I wish this came in an extra small although a small should have been sufficient. Read more
items.author: Pwhirley

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great purchase
items.body: I tried this on the minute it was received. It’s a very pretty soft pink, comfortable, soft, I wear an 8 on top and the medium is great. I love this so much I will consider ordering another one! Read more
items.author: Chantal Marie Doriott

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but sizing inconsistent
items.body: I bought the wine red in a medium, and I loved it - fit perfectly like a true medium and was just the touch of elegance I needed. I loved it enough to buy the same sweater in Khaki, but was bummed when I tried the second one on - the khaki medium was WAY smaller. Luckily, I have a small daughter I can gift this to and save myself the annoyance of a return, but still a bummer! Read more
items.author: J. Ekar

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just buy it! Size down
items.body: Amazing quality! Very good material! Runs a little big. I should've ordered a small. I'm 168 lbs, 5'1" and 36DD. Small would've been perfect Read more
items.author: destin lewis

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Poor quality an terrible fit
items.body: There is no way for me to wear this without the seams looking bulky. I was swimming in a small. I weigh around 135-140. Large chest, hourglass and a small waist. Should have fit a lot better had it been sewn better. Poor craftsmanship. Looks like it could melt in a dryer the fabric seems really cheap. Might not purchase anymore clothes from Amazon based off of recent purchases this one included. Little quality control. Read more
items.author: Ash

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super adorable!
items.body: I was skeptical but this is so incredibly cute on! The back is a tad longer and it drapes perfectly across the front being just short enough but not uncomfortably short. Material is thicker and super soft! Definitely recommend! Read more
items.author: Proud Mom

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Sky Blue, Brown, Blue, Apricot, Army Green, Light Green, Black, Camel, Dark Green, Bright Blue, Wine Red, Khaki, Pink, White. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
